entry.content: I keep telling myself that I'll start singing more and practicing, but I haven't really done so until this week. Being discouraged about not being able to hit the high notes I used to be able to, I've struggled with finding a good range for my voice after it dropped during my transition. I keep the stratchy, patchy notes and "fuck ups" to remind myself that I'm growing as a musician, and everyone is human. It's about the music, not a perfect performance. So, here's a full cover. Love y'all, thanks for listening. #fyp
